Interface LinearGuiContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AttachmentHolder<LinearGuiContainer>, DrawPrioritizeable<LinearGuiContainer>, GuiContainer<LinearGuiContainer>, GuiElement<LinearGuiContainer>, GuiOrientable<LinearGuiContainer>, GuiParent<LinearGuiContainer>

    public interface LinearGuiContainer
extends GuiContainer<LinearGuiContainer>, GuiOrientable<LinearGuiContainer>
    A container that arranges its children one after another vertically or horizontally.
